<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Penguin AI Global</title>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron:wght@400;700;900&family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
*{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
:root{--black:#03050f;--deep:#060c1e;--panel:#0a1228;--border:#1a2d5a;--cyan:#00d4ff;--violet:#7b3fe4;--white:#e8f4ff;--muted:#6a84aa}
body{background:var(--black);color:var(--white);font-family:Arial,sans-serif}
nav{position:fixed;top:0;left:0;right:0;height:60px;background:rgba(3,5,15,.95);border-bottom:1px solid var(--border);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;padding:0 5vw;z-index:100}
.logo{color:var(--white);text-decoration:none;font-weight:900;font-size:1.1rem;letter-spacing:.05em}
.logo span{color:var(--cyan)}
.btn{background:var(--cyan);color:#000;padding:.5rem 1.2rem;border-radius:6px;text-decoration:none;font-weight:700;font-size:.8rem}
.hero{min-height:100vh;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;text-align:center;padding:80px 5vw 60px;background:radial-gradient(ellipse at 50% 30%,rgba(123,63,228,.3),transparent 60%)}
.hero h1{font-size:clamp(2.5rem,7vw,5rem);font-weight:900;line-height:1.1;margin-bottom:1rem;letter-spacing:-.02em}
.hero h1 span{color:var(--cyan)}
.hero p{color:var(--muted);font-size:1.05rem;max-width:500px;margin:0 auto 2rem;line-height:1.7}
.hero-btns{display:flex;gap:1rem;justify-content:center;flex-wrap:wrap}
.btn-main{background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--violet),#0088bb);color:#fff;padding:.85rem 2rem;border-radius:8px;text-decoration:none;font-weight:700;font-size:.9rem}
.btn-out{border:1.5px solid var(--border);color:var(--white);padding:.85rem 1.8rem;border-radius:8px;text-decoration:none;font-weight:600;font-size:.9rem}
section{padding:80px 5vw}
.inner{max-width:1000px;margin:0 auto}
h2{font-size:clamp(1.8rem,3vw,2.5rem);font-weight:900;margin-bottom:.75rem;text-align:center}
.ey{color:var(--cyan);font-size:.75rem;letter-spacing:.15em;text-transform:uppercase;text-align:center;margin-bottom:.5rem}
.sub{color:var(--muted);text-align:center;max-width:500px;margin:0 auto 3rem;line-height:1.7}
.grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(210px,1fr));gap:1px;background:var(--border);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:14px;overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:3rem}
.card{background:var(--deep);padding:1.8rem 1.5rem}
.card-icon{font-size:1.8rem;margin-bottom:.7rem}
.card-title{color:var(--cyan);font-size:.82rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.08em;text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:.5rem}
.card-text{color:var(--muted);font-size:.85rem;line-height:1.6}
.ca-box{background:var(--panel);border:1px solid var(--border);border-radius:12px;padding:1.5rem 2rem;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:space-between;gap:1rem;flex-wrap:wrap}
.ca-box code{color:var(--cyan);font-size:.82rem;word-break:break-all}
.cp{background:var(--cyan);color:#000;border:none;padding:.6rem 1.2rem;border-radius:6px;font-weight:700;font-size:.75rem;cursor:pointer;white-space:nowrap}
footer{border-top:1px solid var(--border);padding:40px 5vw;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:1rem}
.fb{font-weight:900}
.fb span{color:var(--cyan)}
.ft{color:var(--muted);font-size:.8rem}
.xl{color:var(--muted);text-decoration:none;font-size:.85rem}
.xl:hover{color:var(--cyan)}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<nav>
  <a class="logo" href="#">PENGUIN <span>AI GLOBAL</span></a>
  <a class="btn" href="#contract">Buy Token 🚀</a>
</nav>
<section class="hero">
  <div>
    <div style="font-size:.75rem;letter-spacing:.15em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--cyan);margin-bottom:1rem">● Live on Solana</div>
    <h1>PENGUIN <span>AI</span><br>GLOBAL</h1>
    <p>The Future of AI on Solana. Community-driven. Fair launch. Built for everyone.</p>
    <div class="hero-btns">
      <a class="btn-main" href="#contract">Buy $PENGUINAI 🚀</a>
      <a class="btn-out" href="#roadmap">Roadmap</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section id="about" style="background:rgba(0,212,255,.02)">
  <div class="inner">
    <div class="ey">Who We Are</div>
    <h2>About Penguin AI Global</h2>
    <p class="sub">Community-first AI project on Solana. No VCs. No insiders. Just believers building the future of AI together.</p>
    <div class="grid">
      <div class="card"><div class="card-icon">🤖</div><div class="card-title">AI Powered</div><p class="card-text">Real AI tools for token holders.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><div class="card-icon">⚡</div><div class="card-title">Solana Fast</div><p class="card-text">65,000 TPS. Near-zero fees.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><div class="card-icon">🐧</div><div class="card-title">Community</div><p class="card-text">Fair launch. Every holder has a voice.</p></div>
      <div class="card"><div class="card-icon">🔒</div><div class="card-title">Transparent</div><p class="card-text">Open contract. Everything on-chain.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section id="roadmap">
  <div class="inner">
    <div class="ey">The Path Forward</div>
    <h2>Roadmap</h2>
    <p class="sub">Four phases to build and grow the ecosystem.</p>
    <div class="grid">
      <div class="card"><div class="card-icon">🚀</div><div class="card-title">Phase 01 — Launch</div><p class="card-text">Branding · Social media · Community</p></div>
      <div class="card"><div class="card-icon">💎</div><div class="card-title">Phase 02 — Token</div><p class="card-text">Solana launch · Listings · Marketing</p></div>
      <div class="card"><div class="card-icon">🤖</div><div class="card-title">Phase 03 — AI</div><p class="card-text">AI tools · Partnerships · Growth</p></div>
      <div class="card"><div class="card-icon">🌐</div><div class="card-title">Phase 04 — Global</div><p class="card-text">Integrations · Cross-chain · Worldwide</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section id="contract" style="background:rgba(0,212,255,.02)">
  <div class="inner" style="text-align:center">
    <div class="ey">On-Chain</div>
    <h2>Contract Address</h2>
    <p class="sub">Always verify the CA before purchasing.</p>
    <div class="ca-box">
      <code>4fDMSB3RnZfYy34dXfqupkjRkAMtCDgN439NJSfyMez1</code>
      <button class="cp" onclick="navigator.clipboard.writeText('4fDMSB3RnZfYy34dXfqupkjRkAMtCDgN439NJSfyMez1').then(()=>{this.textContent='✓ Copied!';setTimeout(()=>this.textContent='Copy CA',1500)})">Copy CA</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<footer>
  <div><div class="fb">PENGUIN <span>AI GLOBAL</span></div><div class="ft">Building the future of AI on Solana 🐧🚀 · © 2026</div></div>
  <a class="xl" href="https://x.com/PenguinAIGlobal" target="_blank">@PenguinAIGlobal</a>
</footer>
</body>
</html>
